        "uid": "113146"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t因为开国皇帝是爱新觉罗·希特勒泽东。现任皇帝叫叶赫那拉·东条近平<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjZmNDJlYzJiZDI5YmJiMzhjMTFjLnBuZz93aWR0aD01NDImaGVpZ2h0PTY4MA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b6f42ec2bd29bbb38c11c.png?width=542&amp;height=680\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b6f42ec2bd29bbb38c11c.png?width=542&amp;height=680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b6f42ec2bd29bbb38c11c.png?width=542&amp;height=680\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTYzYTg1OWQxNmU4NjQ4N2NhYjBjLmpwZz93aWR0aD0zMDAmaGVpZ2h0PTE2OA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e63a859d16e86487cab0c.jpg?width=300&amp;height=168\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e63a859d16e86487cab0c.jpg?width=300&amp;height=168\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e63a859d16e86487cab0c.jpg?width=300&amp;height=168\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
      "date": "2023-08-09",
      "agree_count": 3,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "677718",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "fk007",
        "uid": "75717"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t说没被清算，其实不太严谨。不是非得像黄巢对待五姓七望一样全部杀光才算是被清算。<br/>\n<br/>\n溥仪没有直系后代，所以直接控制他就够了。<br/>\n要是像以前的帝王一样有十几二十个子女，那可能手段又不一样。<br/>\n<br/>\n强迫满人改汉姓，让以前的皇族平民化，这也算是一种清算。<br/>\n两三代下来，还有几个会记得自己姓爱新觉罗叶赫那拉，还会有几个能体会到这几个姓所代表的荣光？<br/>\n<br/>\n更别说文革里的实质清算。<br/>\n那十年里整死了多少满人贵族，现在都没法统计。<br/>\n<br/>\n再加上计划生育。<br/>\n头胎生了女儿的，这支就算灭族了。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-08-08",
      "agree_count": 3,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
